libexif: libexif (EXIF Tag Parsing Library)
libexif:
libexif: Most digital cameras produce EXIF files, which are JPEG files with 
libexif: extra tags that contain information about the image. The EXIF library 
libexif: allows you to parse an EXIF file and read the data from those tags.
libexif: 
libexif: https://sourceforge.net/projects/libexif
